```After-Hours Logon Activity — extracts the hour from each successful logon and filters
to before 7 AM or after 7 PM. After-hours service-account activity is normal; after-hours
interactive or RDP logons from regular users warrant a closer look.```

index=windows_logs sourcetype=WinEventLog:Security EventCode=4624
| eval hour=strftime(_time, "%H")
| where hour < 7 OR hour > 19
| table _time, Account_Name, Workstation_Name, Logon_Type
| sort -_time
